pycrypto

[1]pycrypto
pycrypto是用Python寫的加解密套件。

This is a collection of both secure hash functions (such as SHA256 and RIPEMD160), 
and various encryption algorithms (AES, DES, RSA, ElGamal, etc.).

https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pycrypto

【安裝Installation】

[1]下載pycrypto的最新版本
位址為：https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pycrypto

[2]安裝
you can simply run "python setup.py build" to build the package, and "python setup.py install" to install it.

python setup.py build

python setup.py install

